Five Cells MPX Test data

mpx_dataset.Rd

MPX data set of 5 immune cells (link to data resource)

  • 1x CD3 capping stimulated CD4 T cell (RCVCMP0000217)

    Data set: CD3 Stimulated Human PBMCs SCSP v1.0 Kit, Immunology Panel I

  • 1x B cell (RCVCMP0000118)
    1x CD4 T cell (RCVCMP0000487)
    1x CD8 T cell (RCVCMP0000655)

    Data set: 1k Human PBMCs, SCSP v1.0 Kit, Immunology Panel I

  • 1x Migratory CD8 T cell with uropod (RCVCMP0000263)

    Data set: Uropod formation on T cells, SCSP v1.0 Kit, Immunology Panel I

Usage

minimal_mpx_pxl_file()

Value

Path to the PXL file containing a minimal MPX data set used in tests
